# Proposal Row Templates

Exact row format variants for the AskUserQuestion multi-select UI.
Use these templates verbatim — do not improvise the format.

---

## Row Format Variants

### New skill — global scope

```
[NEW@global]     {{NAME}}     {{ONE_LINE_REASON}}
```

Example:
```
[NEW@global]     ts-monorepo-scaffold     Multi-step repo bootstrap (criterion 1)
```

### New skill — local scope

```
[NEW@local]      {{NAME}}     {{ONE_LINE_REASON}}
```

Example:
```
[NEW@local]      deploy-staging     Repo-specific deploy pipeline (criterion 2)
```

### Update existing skill — published

```
[UPDATE→{{TARGET}}]     {{TARGET}}     {{ONE_LINE_REASON}}
```

Example:
```
[UPDATE→skila]     skila     Added staging tier docs (criterion 1, minor bump)
```

### Update existing skill — staging tier

```
[UPDATE→{{TARGET}}@staging]     {{TARGET}}     {{ONE_LINE_REASON}} (currently in staging)
```

Example:
```
[UPDATE→my-workflow@staging]     my-workflow     Fix lint step (patch bump, in staging)
```

### Row with lint warning

Append `(WARN: <reason>)` inline:

```
[NEW@global]     {{NAME}}     {{ONE_LINE_REASON}} (WARN: description <40 chars)
```

---

## Wave-1 Overflow Row

When > 8 candidates pass the criteria, collapse excess into:

```
[+{{N}} more low-confidence candidates omitted]
```

Example:
```
[+3 more low-confidence candidates omitted]
```

